      "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
      "body": "Bandwidth usage on mainnet is a bit higher than I'd like -- seems to be comparable to INV traffic. Currently exploring using minisketch to reduce how much data is needed to describe a template update.",
      "user": {
        "login": "ajtowns",
